76561198116210937,Recommended,312280,29448287,Posted: 23 January,all,grinningchimera2,"A great computer chess game. I only have 2 critisisms of this free game. Firstly when playing online against a friend a number of times with the opening move it will not register on the other persons screen meaning we have to restart the game. Not too much of a problem because it only ever seems to happen for the first move, but still annoying. My other issue that has been addressed by others in the review section, is the ability to have multiple queens of the same colour on the board at one time. It is my understanding that when a pawn reaches the far side of the board that player gets to select a previously captured piece from the opponent. This means the game becomes less about tactics and more of a race to the other side to get another queen.But apart from these 2 issues I have this still the best chess game on steam. And it's free. 8/10"
